{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban single-sex associations and clubs",
        "additional_details": "Currently the Equality Act allows associations or clubs to restrict membership to persons who share a protected characteristic, including being men or women.\r\n\r\n\r\nI want this legislation amended so that associations and clubs cannot restrict their membership on the basis of sex.\r\n",
        "background": "We believe there should be no such things as clubs or associations that restrict membership on the basis of sex. I find it appalling and extremely sexist that these sorts of associations exists in modern society.\r\n",
